title: IAA Tonight | Dolphins Upset Bills AND Pat Mahomes argues with Eric Bieniemy
description: Leger Douzable, Omar Kelly and Adam Pac-Man Jones discuss the Miami Dolphins upsetting the Buffalo Bills in Week 3. Discussion includes the concussion protocols in the NFL as Dolphins QB Tua Tagovailoa returned to the game after what was thought to be a concussion. The guys also discuss the on-field disagreement between Chiefs QB Pat Mahomes and assistant head coach Eric Bieniemy.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Omar Kelly, Adam Pac-Man Jones)
